                    time and date of your use of the Service, and other statistics.we dont save or upload any
                    contact data on server.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!--*********************-->
            <div class="title-rw">
                <h2 class="title">Cookies</h2>
                <div class="title-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="paragraph">
                <p>
                    A "cookie" is a small piece of information stored by a web server on a web browser so it can be
                    later read back from that browser. RechargeZap uses cookie and tracking technology depending on
                    the features offered. No personal information will be collected via cookies and other tracking
