                </p>
            </div>
            <!--*********************-->
            <div class="title-rw">
                <h2 class="title">Security</h2>
                <div class="title-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="paragraph">
                <p>
                    RechargeZap has stringent security measures in place to protect the loss, misuse, and alteration
                    of the information under our control. Whenever you change or access your account information, we
                    offer the use of a secure server. Once your information is in our possession we adhere to strict
                    security guidelines, protecting it against unauthorized access.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!--*********************-->
            <div class="title-rw">
                <h2 class="title">Consent</h2>
                <div class="title-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="paragraph">
                <p>
